title._content: View South Up the Delta River Drainage. Pipeline Route Runs on East (Left) Side of River between Richardson Highway and the River Bank...08/1973

description._content: Original Caption: View South Up the Delta River Drainage. Pipeline Route Runs on East (Left) Side of River between Richardson Highway and the River Bank.
